OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine evening towards the southeast,
OL,7,Fbut remaining rather cloudy across the
OL,8,Fnorth, which will spread
OL,9,Fsoutheastwards overnight. Some light
OL,10,Frain and drizzle possible over the
OL,11,Fhills, but most places staying dry.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a cloudy start, cloud
OL,14,Fwill start to lift and break through
OL,15,Fthe morning. Prolonged sunny spells
OL,16,Fwill develop with some warm sunshine
OL,17,Fduring the afternoon, particularly in
OL,18,Fthe south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
